      "content": "hey, im prepping for my debate tournament next week and im stuck. the topic is illegal immigration. basically, which side do you think is more morally defensible: the one focusing on border security and national sovereignty, or the one focusing on humanitarian asylum and human rights? like, which one actually holds more weight morally?",
